Package: ScrSTCs
Title: Inference of human senescent tumor cells from high-throughput single cell RNA-seq data based on senescence marker genes
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
       person("Jiayi", 'Yang', email='yjybio@163.com', role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: SCRSTCS is a computational tool using  marker genes of aging combined with multinomial distribution models and maximum likelihood function principles to identify senescent tumor cells in high-throughput single cell RNA-seq data.
Encoding: UTF-8
